movement in <LOCATION> China </LOCATION> because the protesters `` are linked to us by blood, in their fight for freedom, democracy and survival.'' Also today, the party's newly appointed Secretary-General <PERSON> James </PERSON> <PERSON> Soong </PERSON> told delegates <LOCATION> Taiwan </LOCATION> never will use force to reunify <LOCATION> China </LOCATION>. `` The reunified <LOCATION> China </LOCATION> we are seeking shall be guided by the free will of all the Chinese and the principles of democracy,'' said <PERSON> Soong </PERSON>.
