ndition he receive a psychological evaluation and be treated if authorities recommended it. On Thursday, <PERSON> Linares </PERSON> was taken to <PERSON> Mac </PERSON> <PERSON> Neal </PERSON> after suffering a violent reaction to PCP, an illegal drug also known as angel dust.
